places that players enjoy and talk about.

34
00:02:51,913 --> 00:02:55,756
All of that while trying to go as in-depth as I can in 60 minutes.

35
00:02:57,517 --> 00:02:59,719
I should define what I mean when I say a level,

36
00:03:00,139 --> 00:03:04,682
what a level designer at Arcane Lyon does and what I feel makes a

37
