39
00:03:14,693 --> 00:03:18,556
or a location in the game world, or a moment in the player's journey.

40
00:03:19,417 --> 00:03:24,221
At Arcane Léon, a level designer is defining the layout and flow of the map,

41
00:03:24,801 --> 00:03:28,444
crafting encounters and vignettes with all of the scripted logic that powers them,

42
