character artists, and riggers.

531
00:31:55,482 --> 00:31:56,964
What is the size of an NPC?

532
00:31:57,665 --> 00:31:58,766
How wide is their collision?

533
00:31:58,846 --> 00:32:00,869
How far off the ground is their vision cone?

