615
00:36:27,693 --> 00:36:33,397
Tools can be created to help level designers visualize the more abstract metrics like audio

616
00:36:33,437 --> 00:36:34,377
propagation limits.

617
00:36:35,078 --> 00:36:38,980
You can try to find a balance between the performance cost of some of the rendering

618
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:42,403
